 for man<br><br>        And so you shall begin your destiny, to create a shard of light<br>        You shall seek the Hidden Treasure of the Green Sages<br>        You shall search the home of Knights of all ages<br>        You shall quest for the Uncrowned and Unbounded<br>        You shall find the forgotten and destroy the Barrier<br>        You shall know both true and false, both right and wrong<br>        And you shall catch a glimpse of both Future and Past<br>        for your path lies together and separate, to a mortal end.<br><br><br> <p><b>Segal SoulSaver</b><br>Lead DM - <a href="http://pub26.ezboard.com/bapex71990">Shroud World</a> <BR>A NWN Persistent Campaign<BR><i>And so it was that the gods gifted upon mortal men the varied treasures and mankind was changed for the better and worse, but forever changed. </i></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub26.ezboard.com/usegalsoulsaver.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Segal SoulSaver</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://wwp.icq.com/scripts/online.dll?icq=112539253&img=5" BORDER=0> at: 1/18/02 9:33:59 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#97694F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub26.ezboard.com/usegalsoulsaver.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Segal SoulSaver</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://wwp.icq.com/scripts/online.dll?icq=112539253&img=5" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Lead-GM</span><br>  Posts: 3470<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(3/25/02 2:50:10 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub26.ezboard.com/fapex71990frm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=184.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Words of Papon</span><hr size=1> 5th Chapter, Verses 6 and 7<br><br><br>Upon the land a great calling stirred, primal and preordained<br>The Moon Hider and Blood Abiders look to fate rearranged<br>God touched, or God Born, or God Created, seek the first city<br>Time has past for council, no plans in place for piety or pity<br>Shadows of the forgotten will be recalled, doors opened<br>Red Rulers will seek law in chaos, doors closed<br><br>Servants of the Magi will barter the shards<br>Ghostly guardians still serve loyal in hidden lairs<br>Riddles bar the way, answered by the teeth of clay<br>Chambered riches of the old way wait a new day<br>Five score crescent marked protect the prize<br>Immortals awaiting the ‘Dara Na Docili”<br><br><br><br> <p><b>Segal SoulSaver</b><br>Lead DM - <a href="http://Shroudworld.com">Shroud World</a> <BR>A NWN Persistent Campaign<BR><i>And so it was that the gods gifted upon mortal men the varied treasures and mankind was changed for the better and worse, but forever changed. </i></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub26.ezboard.com/fapex71990frm19.showPrevMessage?topicID=184.topic"> <img src="http://www.nutrocker.co.uk/board/blPrevTopic12.gif" border=0></a><a href="http://pub26.ezboard.com/fapex71990frm19.showNextMessage?topicID=184.topic"> <img src="http://www.nutrocker.co.uk/board/blNextTopic12.gif" border=0> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub26.ezboard.com/fapex71990frm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=184.topic&index=1><img src=http://www.nutrocker.co.uk/board/blAddReply12.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub26.ezboard.com/fapex71990frm19.emailToFriend?topicID=184.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub26.ezboard.com/fapex71990frm19.threadControl?topicID=184.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/deleteThreadFire.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub26.ezboard.co